    <h1>About StudentDesk</h1>
    <p><strong>StudentDesk</strong> is a mini portal for college students to download previous year question papers and important notes for all branches and years.</p>

    <h2>What you can do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Find exam papers filtered by branch, year, semester, and exam type.</li>
      <li>Download high-quality notes PDFs uploaded by faculty or toppers.</li>
      <li>Track which resources are most popular using download counts.</li>
      <li>Students can create a simple account using their roll number.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Who can upload?</h2>
    <p>Only <strong>admins</strong> can upload or delete resources. Students can browse and download, ensuring that the content on the portal is clean and verified.</p>

    <h2>Tech stack</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Node.js + Express.js (backend)</li>
      <li>EJS templating (frontend views)</li>
      <li>MongoDB / MongoDB Atlas (database)</li>
      <li>Multer for PDF uploads</li>
    </ul>

